{"tid":939473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"看準色慾市場　剪髮被巨乳撞果然聚人心","createTime":"2018-12-13T07:18:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T10:06:36.000Z","uid":32511,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"fe0d22b62f2079828a9fa3967e88da0d31c639d7","tid":939473,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T07:18:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CPjnGAR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCPjnGAR.png&h=7e3a9fec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e6xpauc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe6xpauc.png&h=81d08405&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rWxHGAU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrWxHGAU.png&h=b15f0398&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5efmW9f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5efmW9f.png&h=877baf01&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9OO7SHA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9OO7SHA.png&h=26a66b95&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vk1dOfW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvk1dOfW.png&h=a31ee0c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n泰國一間剪髮店「Happy Cut」(快樂剪)，最近推出一組宣傳廣告，標榜有巨乳美髮師為客人服務，讓客人一邊享受理髮、一邊又被大奶撞的樂趣。<br />\n <br />\n    據泰國《khaosod》報導，實際上這是「快樂剪」聘請模特兒與攝影公司，製作的一組宣傳照，巨乳果然聚人心，廣告一推出即刻奏效，「快樂剪」立刻引發網友關注，詢問度也變高。其實「快樂剪」是間正常的闔家歡美髮店，但為了拉抬業績與知名度，店家看準「色慾市場」，直接推出巨乳美髮師廣告，吸引更多顧客上門。<br />\n <br />\n    不僅店家的詢問度變高，就連宣傳照中的男主角，也意外成為網友話題。一名網友桑卡朗(Sornsawan Sangkadklang)自稱就是照片中的男主角，他說不少人羨慕他一邊刮鬍子，一邊被奶撞，他強調當時只是被找去拍照的，之後看到照片的效果，他也感到震撼。"},{"pid":"0a6690ca1a8e2bc68f31186cc1861e4b2d034fe8","tid":939473,"uid":83328,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T07:21:56.000Z","msg":"尾二果張咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd779ef76cc5879dc95ab3b82c0d4a30d768879e","tid":939473,"uid":1713,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T07:22:45.000Z","msg":"不了"},{"pid":"c56750a4c1b54cf3e426541e15c24b1a96f48102","tid":939473,"uid":77233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"0a6690ca1a8e2bc68f31186cc1861e4b2d034fe8","tid":939473,"uid":83328,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T07:21:56.000Z","msg":"尾二果張咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T07:25:17.000Z","msg":"現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b49966867103a6dde676f0022576ff0d0387f45","tid":939473,"uid":137999,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T07:26:57.000Z","msg":"被巨孔撞之餘會被巨龍撞多下"},{"pid":"59582205f534664ff673931151637748dd897688","tid":939473,"uid":36065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T07:27:33.000Z","msg":"假架d奶"},{"pid":"bf81539383d498185f3a9e20e2217a6ae46873f4","tid":939473,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T07:33:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01bed336a6829afe2841fa76d2d3b8ccb642b4a","tid":939473,"uid":212026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T07:33:46.000Z","msg":"人妖假奶"},{"pid":"278b02bb742ece7444ea92ac6f5f578f72a5f376","tid":939473,"uid":24140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T08:36:36.000Z","msg":"U 竟然係個boy!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107729ee90b82da07720c1e91426d75db738881c","tid":939473,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0a6690ca1a8e2bc68f31186cc1861e4b2d034fe8","tid":939473,"uid":83328,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-13T07:21:56.000Z","msg":"尾二果張